Grew up during the height of the castlevania genre so this is a perfect fit;
Graphically its very divisive; you either like the jpegs or you dont.
there's always something to level up or grind for, but (ignoring the optional area's) you can beat the stages through skill alone, Then again im only playing on hard; cant speak for impossible difficulty.
